(33932, 577, 'persons_12_person_description', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Andreas Weiss is the Vice President of Platform Solutions at GBM, responsible for the company’s Hardware Business Unit and leading GBM’s system solutions for Private and Hybrid Cloud. He is also in charge of IT optimization, consolidation and virtualization for our clients.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Andreas brings more than 26 years of IT industry knowledge from across over 50 countries. Prior to joining GBM, Andreas worked with IBM in a variety of roles, spanning sales, marketing and brand management. During his time at IBM, he managed and excelled the Storage Business Unit for the company in Central Europe and the Middle East with sustainable growth.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Andreas holds a Master of Arts degree in Economics from San Francisco State University and a Diplom Kaufmann (MBA) degree from University of Tuebingen in Germany.</p>'),
