(34334, 1142, 'careers_card_content', 'The high performance culture at GBM isn’t about how many hours we put in. It’s about working smarter together, developing the right skills and reaching goals we all help define.\r\n\r\nWe believe the team that is most empowered, that loves what they do, is the team that achieves the most success.\r\n\r\nWe are a diverse and global group, but we share key values: passionate about digital transformation, committed to excellence, and willing to go the extra mile.'),
