(19165, 847, 'careers_page_article', '<em>Employment Type: Permanent</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Language Skills: English and Arabic</em>\r\n\r\n<b>Job Summary</b>\r\n\r\nThe position is for a Security Consultant who can Position GBM Security Framework to clients and build GBM Security Brand\r\nin Qatar.\r\n\r\n<b>Qualifications Required</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bachelor Degree in Engineering</li>\r\n 	<li>Minimum 8 years of experience in Security Practice.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
