(21562, 898, 'about_partners_0_description', 'As the first authorised SI for the country, GBM will offer a range of services and hardware to deploy Apple solutions, with a focus on integrated mobility solutions. GBM will provide dedicated Apple business strategy, consultancy, as well as implementation services.\r\n\r\nPhilippe Jarre, chief executive officer of GBM, stated: \"GBM has a 26-year heritage of partnering with leaders in the global IT industry. As we continue our transformation journey at GBM, our collaboration with Apple is a commitment to bringing further innovations to our customers, delivering more value to our stakeholders and enriching the market with a new set of solutions.\"'),
