(34268, 1141, 'persons_9_person_description', 'Susanne Peter is the Chief Financial Officer of Gulf Business Machines (GBM). She is responsible for the financial strategy and operations of GBM and its branches in the UAE, Bahrain, Kuwait, Oman, Qatar, and Pakistan.\r\nSusanne joined GBM in October 2016. Prior to this, she was the Vice President of Finance for IBM Germany, Austria, and Switzerland, where she led the financial operations across all three of these markets. During her 30+ years with IBM, she held various other CFO and VP positions in different business units. Susanne has accumulated a wealth of experience in Growth Markets and Global Headquarter roles and has worked with multiple regions closely, having done stints in Germany, France, the United States, Austria, Ireland, and the Middle East.\r\n\r\nSusanne earned her degree in Business Administration from Heilbronn University in Germany.'),
