(32389, 1101, 'summary_text', 'The brightest talents from 46 countries combine their skills as part of the 1,200-strong GBM team.\r\n\r\nWe believe work must be challenging, rewarding and fun. We provide excellent employee benefits and training, plus the opportunity to work with cutting-edge technologies. Because inspired people create better solutions.\r\n\r\nIf you are passionate about building the digital future, join us.'),
